@jinmeiliao I've made a few changes. Added GeodeClusterManagementServiceBuilder which is specifically geared towards the Geode Cache CMS configuration. The current ClusterManagementServiceBuilder is specifically targeted to a non-Cache CMS builder.
I've also added GeodeConnectionConfig and cleaned up the BaseConnectionConfig / ConnectionConfig confusion.
I hope that my latest refactor will not force the user to know about RestTemplate..... Transport. You can still create your own Transport and add it using setTransport

